{"tid":1559040,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[召喚發明家]岀屎淋狗 有冇得諗","createTime":"2019-09-10T16:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T16:22:21.000Z","uid":313902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9bc0f7f4e2fddcb80cedf8fa469812fb3831a7aa","tid":1559040,"uid":313902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:04:15.000Z","msg":"之前有巴打話用屎沐狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港幾百間動物醫院一日咁多有機材料<br />\n啲狗屁又整喊貓貓 係時候全港動物界大行動<br />\n喂狗狗食啲健康有機產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於點樣發射狗糧<br />\n有冇IT巴打諗下點樣善用無人機 高空放糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n優先喂比最癲嘅唐狗食 一日服用兩次 都夠晒數<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班狗肯定食到hi晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貓貓食到有機產品有得換衫 但聽講狗狗3好難換<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但要諗下承重量 <br />\n防tracker <br />\n點樣command放軍糧<br />\n 最好就機身防埋彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efbc812fe9ef6a0257d50a26f3b9d08be0556a56","tid":1559040,"uid":7045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:08:09.000Z","msg":"你玩屎時 新屋嶺果班只會食得更多"},{"pid":"4bfc6f0db0470d3d1d5a4f57bf7a33fb41133064","tid":1559040,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:22:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558977</a>"}]}